You are working on TaskMaster Pro backend MVP.

Coding standards:
- Keep architecture layered: routes -> controllers -> services -> repositories.
- Keep controllers thin and business logic in services.
- Access Prisma only in repository layer.
- Validate external input with Zod.
- Use async/await and avoid callback style.
- Keep error responses in this format:
  {
    "success": false,
    "message": "Error message"
  }
